The Minister of State Security, Adv Bongani Bongo, MP, is in Addis Ababa, Ethiopia, as part of the delegation of South African Ministers supporting HE President Zuma who is attending the AU Summit for Heads of State and Government. The Summit, which is scheduled for 28 and 29 January 2018, is held under the theme: Winning the fight against corruption: A sustainable path to Africa's transformation. Issued by: State Security Agency